Rip notes: removed the David Bowie FMV

Responding to the desperate pleas of a mysterious character from another dimension, your soul must enter the futuristic city of Omikron. Think, fight and interact with the immense gaming gaming environment to defeat the menacing demons that have tried to trap you.
- a huge living environment in real time 3D with hundreds of passers by and vehicle to interact with
- original soundtrack by David Bowie and Reeves Gabrels
- 220 minutes of dialogue with real time facial motion capture.